<s> <s> postulating some generalization as the goal of the movement of humanity , the historians study the men of whom the greatest number of monuments have remained: kings , ministers , generals , authors , reformers , popes , and journalists , to the extent to which in their opinion these persons have promoted or hindered that abstraction . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> history proves this at every turn . </s> </s> 
