<s> <s> arriving at this conclusion we can reply directly and positively to these two essential questions of history: </s> </s> 
<s> <s> ( 1 ) what is power? </s> </s> 
<s> <s> ( 1 ) power is the relation of a given person to other individuals , in which the more this person expresses opinions , predictions , and justifications of the collective action that is performed , the less is his participation in that action . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> or in other words , the conception of a cause is inapplicable to the phenomena we are examining . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> electricity produces heat , heat produces electricity . </s> </s> 
